    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You gave me life but where’s... my sight?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am still blind and that’s... my plight"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Blind lead the blind and then... both fall"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So right now on You... I call"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus have mercy on me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Open my eyes that I might see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All I know is my only hope is in You."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord I am rebuked by... the crowd"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For You I cry out more... the loud"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the world wants to di...stract me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So I forget that I... can’t see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus don’t leave me behind"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You are the one I want to find"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All I know is I just really need You."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Still I’m afraid that You’ll... go on"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But joyful ears hear You... respond"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What would You like for me... to do"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh Christ I just want to see You"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Open my eyes to... see You"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let me find what my spirit can do"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All I know is I just want to see You."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In my spirit I... can see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Because that’s where You... touch me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By Your touch dear Lord... I’m healed"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All my sin and death... must yield"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now Lord, I am healed"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In my spirit You are so real"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All I know is I want to keep touching You."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord my sight is for... one thing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So that I to You... can cling"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I think I’m in love... with You"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No one else for me... will do"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Christ let me follow You please"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’re so real and so special to me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All I know is Lord I never want to leave."
            }
          ]
        }
